description:
The Rugged Commander by VS for Men is the ideal grooming tool for taming beard & stubble, thanks to diamond sharpened blades that allow for a smooth, clean-cut finish and a 30 minute cordless runtime. This trimmer is packed with all the essentials for trimming at-home or on-the-go.

Product Features:

Multi-use full size trimmer
Trim beard, moustache, goatee and more
Diamond sharpened blades for a smooth clean-cut finish
Rechargeable - 30min cordless run time
3x Position trimming settings 0.6mm, 1.1mm and 1.5mm
5 Position comb guide ranging from 2mm to 10mm
Cleaning brush and oil included
2x Stubble comb guides
name: Vs Sassoon Rugged Commander Beard And Stubble Trimmer 1EA
